data.description: $8300 SELLER CONCESSION with full price offer can be used for closing costs or to BUY DOWN THE INTEREST RATE.  Boasting a spacious yard complete with a greenhouse, two storage sheds, and a raised garden bed, this home is a green thumb's paradise. The attached garage is a rare bonus at this price point, making parking and storage a breeze. Inside, you'll find an updated interior with newer windows, sleek tile floors in the kitchen, and cozy carpeting in the living room and bedrooms. The bathroom has undergone a gorgeous remodel. Additional features include new gutters, solar panels for energy efficiency, captivating jellyfish lighting, new screen and security doors. Enjoy the ease of daily life with nearby grocery stores and hassle-free highway access, simplifying your commute and enabling quick trips to all your favorite destinations. Don't miss out on this perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and natural beauty.
